        "detailedDescription_md": "The Labor Department of Chhattisgarh introduced the &quot;Dhobhi Hetu Avashyak Upkaran Sahayata Yojana&quot; on January 10, 2018, through the &quot;Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board.&quot; Under this scheme, the washerman is provided with materials worth Rs. 1,500/-, including electronic/coal iron, clothespins, and a washing paddle (Thappi/Kutela).\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- Provided materials worth ₹1,500/-, including electronic/coal iron, clothespins, and a washing paddle (Thappi/Kutela).\n\n",
